title: Dr Fauci Interview and more
itunes:title: Dr Fauci Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we ran back our interview we had with Dr. Fauci where he gave us some more update on the Corona Virus and what the trump administration is doing to combat it and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Stephen Moore to comparing people protesting to Rosa Parks. Moreover, we also had author and medicine advocate Deepak Chopra call up and spoke on how to cope with everything going on in today's world
